title: EyeConnect 1.5.1
description:
EyeConnect software enables your UPnPTM AV digital media device to stream EyeTV 
recordings, digital photos, music and movies from your Mac onto your TV or stereo.

EyeTV recordings: Watch EyeTV recordings on your TV in the comfort of your living room. 

Pictures: View individual digital photos or your entire iPhotoTM library, on your TV.
